{"lemma":"فَهْد","slug":"فَهْد","root":"ف.ه.د","root_slug":"ف-ه-د","root_link":"/words/roots/ف-ه-د","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun_prop","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["name","noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":3},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n34714","n34715","n34716"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%81%D9%8E%D9%87%D9%92%D8%AF"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"cheetah"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"leopard","tags":["proscribed"]},{"pos":"name","gloss":"a male given name, Fahd or Fahad"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"From فَهْد (fahd, “cheetah”)."},"ipa":["/fahd/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n34714","headword_ar":"فَهِدَ","root":"fhd","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (S, A, O, L, K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (A, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fahadN","text_ar":"فَهَدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (L.)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a man. S, A, O)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"resembled the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fahod","text_ar":"فَهْد"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lynx"},{"kind":"text","text":"] (S, A, O, L, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in his stretching himself and his sleeping."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L, K,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in his much sleeping, and stretching himself."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, O.) And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He slept, and was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"feigned himself, heedless of what was requisite,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"necessary to be done."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L, K.) Hence the saying, (S, L,) of a woman describing her husband, as related in the story of Umm-Zara, (L,)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ino daxala fahida waA_ino xaraja A^asida walaA yasoA^alu Eam~aA Eahida","text_ar":"اـِنْ دَخَلَ فَهِدَ وَاـِنْ خَرَجَ اَسِدَ وَلَا يَسْاَلُ عَمَّا عَهِدَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, * L,) i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"If he come in"},{"kind":"text","text":"and be with me in the tent, or house,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he is"},{"kind":"text","text":"gentle and quiet"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"like the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fahod","text_ar":"فَهْد"},{"kind":"text","text":", which is described as sleeping much; and is, or feigns himself, heedless of the things that are amiss therein, and that I ought to put into a right, or proper, state; such is his generosity, and goodness of disposition;"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and if he go out,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and see his enemy,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he is like the lion"},{"kind":"text","text":"[in boldness;"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and he will not ask respecting what he has ordered"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (L.) And one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fahidota Ean~iY","text_ar":"فَهِدْتَ عَنِّى"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fahadN","text_ar":"فَهَدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Thou wast,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hast been, heedless,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"negligent, of me."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fahada lahu","text_ar":"فَهَدَ لَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (O, L, K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He did well,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"kindly, in his affair in his absence;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, L, K:) like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faA^ada","text_ar":"فَاَدَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mahada","text_ar":"مَهَدَ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (O, L.)"}],"source_refs":["S","A","O","L","K"]},{"entry_id":"n34715","headword_ar":"فَهْدٌ","root":"fhd","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"[The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lynx; lupus cervarius;"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a well-known beast of prey;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L, Msb, K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with which one hunts; and which sleeps much;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"called in Pers."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yuwzo","text_ar":"يُوزْ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Mgh:) fem."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fahodapN","text_ar":"فَهْدَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (L. Msb:) pl. of the masc."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fuhuwdN","text_ar":"فُهُودٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mgh, O, L, Msb, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^afohudN","text_ar":"اَفْهُدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, L, K) which is a pl. of pauc.; (O:) and the pl. of the fem., accord. to analogy, is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fahadaAtN","text_ar":"فَهَدَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^anowamu mina Alfahodi","text_ar":"اَنْوَمُ مِنَ الفَهْدِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"More sleepful than the lynx"},{"kind":"text","text":"] is a proverb. (A.) ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A nail in the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wAsiT","text_ar":"واسِط"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fore part"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"camel's saddle called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raHol","text_ar":"رَحْل"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (O, L, K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"also termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kalobN","text_ar":"كَلْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.]. (L.) To the creaking sound of this nail the similar sound of a stallion-camel's tushes is likened."}],"source_refs":["Mgh","S","O","L","Msb","K"]},{"entry_id":"n34716","headword_ar":"فَهِدٌ","root":"fhd","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fihido","text_ar":"فِهِدْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[A man]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"resembling the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fahod","text_ar":"فَهْد"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lynx"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in his stretching himself and has sleeping"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in his doing thus much,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"often"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: and [a man]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"being."},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"feigning himself, heedless of what is requisite,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"necessary to be done."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.)"}],"source_refs":[]}]}}